description.en: hiBAYC is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of the target BAYC (or set of BAYCs) in the BAYC Meta-Swap of Fracton Protocol. For each new BAYC added to the collection, the total supply of hiBAYC will increase by 1 million.
